---
import '@/styles/globals.css'
---

<div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-700 via-pink-500 to-red-500">
    <div class="w-full max-w-md overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 border-0 shadow-xl relative rounded-lg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-blue-500 to-purple-600 opacity-30"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 p-6">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">2023</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-200">최신 웹 디자인 트렌드를 반영한 카드 컴포넌트입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-100 mb-4">
            그라데이션, 유리 형태 효과, 네온 색상 등 2023년의 주요 디자인 요소들을 포함하고 있습니다.
          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-2">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-blue-500 rounded-full shadow-neon-blue">
              그라데이션
            </span>
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-purple-500 rounded-full shadow-neon-purple">
              유리 형태
            </span>
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-pink-500 rounded-full shadow-neon-pink">
              네온 효과
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-purple-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-full transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105">
            트렌드 더 알아보기
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <style>
    /* 네온 효과를 위한 추가 스타일 */
    .shadow-neon-blue {
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px #3b82f6, 0 0 20px #3b82f6;
    }
    .shadow-neon-purple {
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px #8b5cf6, 0 0 20px #8b5cf6;
    }
    .shadow-neon-pink {
      box-shadow: 0 0 5px #ec4899, 0 0 20px #ec4899;
    }
  </style>
